revisions.description: PTP670-02-65: Added Secure License Signature Alarm. Renamed ethernet statistics counters for clarity and added ethernet Tx counters. Added erroredSeconds (ES), Severely Errored Seconds (SES) and unavailableSeconds (UAS) to the MIB.

PTP670-02-60: Added DNS feature support. Added ethernet statistics configuration data. Added syncE slave port and overwrite quality level. Added counters for wireless packets transmitted and received. Added installation mode setting. Added SNTP SHA1 configuration support. Added PCB temperature setting. Removed Transparent Clock Source Port Alarm Trap.
PTP670-02-50: Revision with HCMP topology support.
PTP670-02-00: Added encryption algorithms TLS-RSA, TLS-PSK 128 bit and TLS-PSK 256 bits. Deprecated static AES 128-bit and AES 256-bit encryption algorithms. Added Cambium Sync support.
